1949;;Down to the Sea in Ships;;American;;Henry Hathaway;;Richard Widmark, Lionel Barrymore;;adventure;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Down_to_the_Sea_in_Ships_(1949_film);;Whaling ship captain Bering Joy (Lionel Barrymore) takes his grandson Jed (Dean Stockwell) on a whaling expedition in order to teach the young boy real life values such as honesty, courage, wisdom, fairness and hard work. However it is First Mate Lunceford (Richard Widmark) who teaches him about life.